These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | tea | coffee |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Hobby      | reading  | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, biathlon
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Sport   | biathlon    | skateboarding |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
