.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | martial-arts |

