.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, salsa
2 different pets are kept: dog, frog
1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | salsa |
| Pet           | frog       | dog       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-9::.
