.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, corn
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald
1. the person who likes emerald is the person eating corn##1
2. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Food          | corn | blueberry |
| Color   | emerald | ivory   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | december | march   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

